===Etymology===
A calque of the German word ''[[Kommunismus]]'' (from Marx and Engels's ''[http://www.marxists.org/archive/marx/works/1848/communist-manifesto/index.htm Manifesto of the German Communist Party]''), in turn a calque of the French word ''[[communisme]]'', which was formed from ''[[commun]]'' ("common"), from Latin ''[[communis]]'', and the suffix [[-isme]] ("[[-ism]]").

===Noun===
