# A term used to refer to a number of political philosophies or ideologies which share the belief in the virtue of holding the production resources collectively. 
# A society organized in line with the communist theories. According to the theory the ultimate aim is the abolishment of state, but in practice the attempts to create a communist society have led to [[totalitarian]] states.
